  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A multi-site randomized controlled trial where patients are allocated to operative treatment
      or conservative treatment of fractures of the neck of the 5th metacarpal bone. The study goal
      is to identify which degree of angular displacement in the fracture that requires operative
      intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
